posts.title: It has dawned on me as to why ActBlue is shitting their pants right now...
posts.content:
We all know what O'Keefe has uncovered about ActBlue, that they are essentially creating false donors to get around donation limits, by creating thousands of false donors under real names and addresses to funnel large donations under. Now what happens if Kamala can't legally access those raised funds? They have to be sent back to the donors. Right now I'd bet they're cooking the books around the clock as we speak. There's 2 routes....1. They pretend to give the money back and create a bunch of fake transactions, which is a lot of overheard (and will leave a trail), or 2. All that money has to be given "back" to the people they falsely donated under.

They obviously don't want to do that because that means they would lose the money, while also exposing their scheme, because suddenly thousands of people will find they're 10's of thousands of dollars richer overnight, and that would obviously raise some questions they can't answer. So obviously the first option is the way they'd want to go, by pretending they've given the money back and then it was returned to be given to Kamala properly....but even that is a clusterfuck, because there's no way to make those kinds of records look natural, especially when it comes to receiving the money back under donations to Kamala's campaign.

And this is all exactly why they want to avoid this entirely and instead pretend like they can just hand Biden funds off to Kamala, despite it being entirely illegal. This is why Biden dropping out is a huge problem for them because it throws a huge wrench in their donor money laundering scheme. They want to keep this wool over people's eyes going long enough until the election, because they intend to steal it with fraud. If they can't keep the charade up, then they will realize just how bad of an idea it would be to continue with the fraud, because no one is going to believe Kamala actually won with essentially zero campaign funds at her disposal.

This is also why they had to stick behind Kamala, because switching to a different candidate would automatically guarantee they have to refund those fake donations, which they'll never get back, causing the wealthy elites that are really behind the money to lose all of it and outright expose the whole illegal operation.

Whether they do fraud or not depends entirely on if they can keep this illegal election finance fraud from being stopped before the elections. That's why this must be stopped NOW. The GOP and FBI must investigate, and while I have no faith in them, someone needs to do something to catch them in the act, and now is the perfect time because there's no way they can believably cook the books of their fake donor accounts. Money has to come from somewhere, and it leaves a trail, even when it leaves no trail. Times and dates of all donations are also important.

This is why Kamala cannot be allowed to illegally finance her campaign with money raised through Biden. For them to move the campaign money legally by having donors re-donate to Kamala, their financing fraud would be instantly exposed due to all the logistics it would take to do that, which is exactly why they're willing to commit blatant campaign finance violations to keep it from being exposed in full.

posts.title: Message from Ben Garrison
posts.content:
Message from Ben Garrison, u/grrrgraphics :

I thought I’d give everyone an update. Earlier in May I had what I thought would be my final colonoscopy. The surgeon ordered it to happen 1 year after my colon cancer surgery.

I expected to pass and then have my port removed. I thought positive and told the universe I was healthy, etc etc. But no, the doctor found more cancer in a different spot. It’s a different type, too. I didn’t know there was a variety.

My oncologist was blunt and said if I did nothing I would die an excruciatingly painful death. Hmmm…lessee excruciatingly painful death or chemotherapy and radiation. I chose chemo and radiation. I get zapped daily and I take four chemo pills every 12 hours. Come August I will feel the zaps and the chemo, since it will have built up in my system. I don’t know how this will affect cartoon production, but I will do the best I can. THIS is the year for my best cartoons and I have a huge distraction…but as Trump said, we all need to get up and fight. --BG

You can donate to Ben here: https://grrrgraphics.com/product-category/support-ben-garrison-cartoons/
